{"tid":1030300,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗5爪反擊馬體會球迷","createTime":"2019-02-21T00:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:56:49.000Z","uid":199590,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff2260b512e79e520c41b3a1c6fd5bd7b6e4cf9","tid":1030300,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLMSJKG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLMSJKG.jpg&h=5e6f50c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=73047089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度遭馬德里體育會球迷辱罵，伸出5根手指反擊，到底有何含義?<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）周三歐聯16強首回合作客馬德里體育會時，遭到主場球迷辱罵和噓聲對待，一開場宣讀其名字時，已經全場大噓，比賽開始後更是夾雜罵聲。<br />\n<br />\nC朗當然不會善罷甘休，在完半場前伸出5根手指搖晃，有人覺得他表示遭受5次侵犯，但西班牙傳媒表示那代表5個歐聯冠軍和5次金球獎，以此來還擊馬德里體育會球迷的侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n馬體會球迷的辱罵實在有點過分，包括「強姦犯C朗！」、「C朗去死！」無一不是觸及C朗的内心之痛，他未能把憤怒化作入波，最終球隊還以0:2落敗。"},{"pid":"fdec0121e08001ccf70ba53e64f55959c63ad6c2","tid":1030300,"uid":4009,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wHq4jv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wHq4jv.png&h=6eb5bb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nc朗5爪反擊馬體會高甸"},{"pid":"9de2dc3a23b75636ed3df2efca3ef4a5d509f5a6","tid":1030300,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdec0121e08001ccf70ba53e64f55959c63ad6c2","tid":1030300,"uid":4009,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wHq4jv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wHq4jv.png&h=6eb5bb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nc朗5爪反擊馬體會高甸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 